#According to the theories of Karl Marx. This 19th century German philosopher conceived the 'Theory of Social Evolution', otherwise known as 'Historical Materialism'. This theory turned history from mere record-keeping into a science that analyses cultural growth. Marx used the theory to propose that that mankind is evolving through several stages which started with [[Communism]] & will ultimately return there have passed through Classical Society, [[Feudalism]] and [[Capitalism]].

